# This is a manual patch instruction
Replace the ContentLinkXXX components with new components that use the contentLinkAttrs helper from dastro.

## Example in ContentText
Before:
```astro
<ContentLinkGroup class="text ui-richtext">
    <DefaultStructuredText data={data.text} />
  </ContentLinkGroup>
```
After:
```astro
<div class="text ui-richtext" {...contentLinkAttrs({ group: true })}>
   <DefaultStructuredText data={data.text} />
</div>
```
